TV Magazine The thigh's the limit Nicola McLean shows off her endless legs in a loose jumper and thigh high boots as she gets back to reality after Celebrity Big Brother exit 
The WAG momentarily hit a snag as her ripped jumper got caught in her car keys, but held her composure flawlessly before managing to untangle herself By JILL ROBINSON, SHOWBIZ REPORTER 7th February 2017, 9:13 am
